  <entry>
    <title>奔程</title>
    <link href="https://mengnn.cn/2019/07/24/hello-world/"/>
    <id>https://mengnn.cn/2019/07/24/hello-world/</id>
    <published>2019-07-24T07:20:16.320Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-26T08:14:48.690Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>​        今天无意间看到自己很久很久以前写的一首诗，虽然感觉当时的自己很稚嫩，但诗表达的意思非常的直白，也非常的积极向上。最近总是很爱怀旧，也许在怀念曾经“生命不息，奋斗不止”的自己，也许在怀念曾经一起嬉嬉笑笑，吵吵闹闹的朋友们，又或许是在感叹时间的流逝。</p><a id="more"></a><p>​        是呀，也许我们这一代真的老了。很多人说，开始怀旧，意味着你开始变老了，曾经许下的诺言，曾经吹过的牛逼，甚至是曾经自大的写下的文字，好像似乎大概都在啪啪打脸，关键还不承认。这也许是每个人最失败的地方。有人说，你开始走下坡路，说明自己正站在高处，只有高处的人才有下坡路之说，好像是这么个道理，又好像不是。我们是时候看清现实了，从来没有站到过高处，又何来的高处之说，还没努力，怎么就能放弃呢，还没头破血流，怎么就放弃呢，还没无路可走，怎么就放弃了呢。是呀，人生需要拼搏，人生需要经历不平凡。人生就是一段奔程。</p><h2 id="奔程"><a href="#奔程" class="headerlink" title="奔程"></a>奔程</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">一路还有汗流</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">梦想需要坚守</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">命运还没到尽头</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">你我怎能放手</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">也许会有失败</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">也许仍会泪流</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">也许，也许是漫长的等候</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">但，风雨过后</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">就不我们梦圆的时候</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">不要哭泣</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">不再等候</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">有梦的地方</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">就有我们忠诚的追求</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">即使面黄体瘦</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">即使头破血流</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">年轻的我们</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> 一生奋斗</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">只为梦想开花的时候</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;​        今天无意间看到自己很久很久以前写的一首诗，虽然感觉当时的自己很稚嫩，但诗表达的意思非常的直白，也非常的积极向上。最近总是很爱怀旧，也许在怀念曾经“生命不息，奋斗不止”的自己，也许在怀念曾经一起嬉嬉笑笑，吵吵闹闹的朋友们，又或许是在感叹时间的流逝。&lt;/p&gt;
    
